title: Hour 2 Nick Wright on who is to blame in Philly
itunes:title: Hour 2 Nick Wright on who is to blame in Philly
description:
Nick Wright tells Dan that all Sixer's fans are to blame because of unreal expectations placed on the Sixers for this season. Nick Wright says that the Sixers are overrated.
